  "detailed_description": "AI: Art Impostor is the brand new party AI drawing game that you can play with 3-8 players online and enjoy cross-platform play between Android, iOS, and PC!<br><br>You and other AI artists are collaborating for a new exhibition…<br>But one of you is an impostor that doesn't know the exhibition theme.<br>Find out who the impostor is. Or if it's you, fake it 'til you make it!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Simple Rules</h2>- A theme is chosen at random.<br><br>- The theme is shown to the real artists, but not to the impostor!<br>- Each player uses the AI to make drawings and shows them to the other players.<br>- Finally, players vote on who is the impostor.<br>- If the impostor is caught, the artists win!<br>- BUT if the impostor can guess the theme, then the impostor wins!!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2154230/extras/bb68b49664958bc8be3f6eccfb689317.poster.avif?t=1745915662\" width=614 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2154230/extras/bb68b49664958bc8be3f6eccfb689317.webm?t=1745915662\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2154230/extras/bb68b49664958bc8be3f6eccfb689317.mp4?t=1745915662\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Groundbreaking Gameplay</h2>Have you ever tried a game where you can play with AI-generated art?<br><br>Now is your chance to try it out!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2154230/extras/41a5110921573cc8bf3f6068b78a73b0.poster.avif?t=1745915662\" width=614 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2154230/extras/41a5110921573cc8bf3f6068b78a73b0.webm?t=1745915662\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2154230/extras/41a5110921573cc8bf3f6068b78a73b0.mp4?t=1745915662\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >No Need For Artistic Talent</h2>All you need to do is to give the AI a few words or a short sentence related to the theme.<br><br>Then the AI will generate completely unique art for you.<br>You don't need to have aesthetic taste or an artistic background.<br>Sometimes AI-generated arts look weird and strange, but that's a form of art, too.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2154230/extras/82f6b82484d6b107a3037907a1f9435e.poster.avif?t=1745915662\" width=614 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2154230/extras/82f6b82484d6b107a3037907a1f9435e.webm?t=1745915662\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2154230/extras/82f6b82484d6b107a3037907a1f9435e.mp4?t=1745915662\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Cross-Play with Other Players</h2>You can play this game with strangers around the world or with your friends via Room ID.<br><br>Your friends don't have a computer? No problem. You can play this game on a smartphone too.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2154230/extras/fbdda80ff26e4de342828d46dfbb377e.poster.avif?t=1745915662\" width=614 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2154230/extras/fbdda80ff26e4de342828d46dfbb377e.webm?t=1745915662\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2154230/extras/fbdda80ff26e4de342828d46dfbb377e.mp4?t=1745915662\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Short Game Time</h2>It only takes around 5 minutes to play one match.<br><br>Play anytime! You can always sneak in one more round.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2154230/extras/f57a13ad9a987f308a34d2fa162ca3e2.poster.avif?t=1745915662\" width=614 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2154230/extras/f57a13ad9a987f308a34d2fa162ca3e2.webm?t=1745915662\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2154230/extras/f57a13ad9a987f308a34d2fa162ca3e2.mp4?t=1745915662\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Low System Requirement</h2>This game doesn't require an expensive high-spec computer to play.<br><br>You may be able to play this game on an old computer stored in a closet.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2154230/extras/509d9fa1a76836aaa792974b2c470d4a.poster.avif?t=1745915662\" width=614 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2154230/extras/509d9fa1a76836aaa792974b2c470d4a.webm?t=1745915662\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2154230/extras/509d9fa1a76836aaa792974b2c470d4a.mp4?t=1745915662\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Customizability</h2>Choose avatars and styles to stand out in the game!<br><br>※There are two types of items that can be purchased with the in-game currency and the ones purchasable with the In-App Purchase currency.<br>※Currently, the Steam edition doesn't support In-App Purchase and we'll add this feature in a future update.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2154230/extras/ebc7de6d9273f87eef8708a9c82b9d82.poster.avif?t=1745915662\" width=614 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2154230/extras/ebc7de6d9273f87eef8708a9c82b9d82.webm?t=1745915662\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2154230/extras/ebc7de6d9273f87eef8708a9c82b9d82.mp4?t=1745915662\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
